\section{Scope}
\label{sec:scope}
Our research looks at layer 2 topology discovery with the use of LLDP. The layer 2 topology will be correlated with layer 3 topologies based on the protocols such as OSPF, VRF etc. By structuring the layer 3 data provided by these protocols we aim at designing a modular extensible implementation for correlating.

What layer 3 protocols?
VLANS?
